{{Infobox protected area | name = Küre Mountains National Park | alt_name = ''Küre Dağları Milli Parkı'' | iucn_category = | photo = Küre Dağları Güllüce Köyü Kanyonu 2014-06-15 19-58.jpeg | photo_alt = | photo_caption = A view of Güllüce village canyon at Küre Mountains. | photo_width = | map = Turkey | map_alt = | map_caption = | map_width = | relief = yes | label = Küre Mountains NP | label_position = bottom | mark = | marker_size = | location = [[Pınarbaşı, Kastamonu|Pınarbaşı]], [[Cide]], [[Şenpazar]] in [[Kastamonu Province]] - [[Ulus, Bartın|Ulus]] in [[Bartın Province]], Turkey | nearest_city = | coords = {{coord|41|39|20|N|33|09|22|E|region:TR|format=dms|display=inline,title}} | coords_ref = | area = {{convert|37753|ha|abbr=on}} | designation = | authorized = | created = | established = {{start date|2000|07|07}} | designated = | visitation_num = | visitation_year = | visitation_ref = | governing_body = [[Ministry of Forest and Water Management (Turkey)|Ministry of Forest and Water Management]] | administrator = | operator = | owner = | world_heritage_site = | website = {{URL|http://www.milliparklar.gov.tr/mp/kuredaglari/index.htm}} | child = | embedded = }} '''Küre Mountains National Park''' ({{lang-tr|Küre Dağları Milli Parkı}})), established on July 7, 2000, is a [[national park]] in northern Turkey. The national park stretches over the mountain range of [[Küre Mountains]] and is located in the districts [[Pınarbaşı, Kastamonu|Pınarbaşı]], [[Cide]], [[Şenpazar]] in [[Kastamonu Province]] and [[Ulus, Bartın|Ulus]] in [[Bartın Province]].<ref name="mp"/>
It covers an area of {{convert|37753|ha|abbr=on}} at an average elevation of {{convert|500|m|ft|abbr=on}}.<ref name="mp"/>
